## 2. SR Stage-2 Finetuning 준비
- [ ] block4 전용 EO/IR Stage-2 train config 4개 확인
  - `configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_2x_dim32_block4_eo.yaml`
  - `configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_4x_dim32_block4_eo.yaml`
  - `configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_2x_dim32_block4_ir.yaml`
  - `configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_4x_dim32_block4_ir.yaml`
- [ ] 각 config의 `pretrained_path`가 Stage-1 block4 `best.pth`를 가리키는지 확인
- [ ] EO Stage-2는 Denoise 이후 SR 입력 분포 기준으로 `configs/data/sr_finetune_eo_after_denoise.yaml` 사용
- [ ] IR Stage-2 입력 조건 결정
  - [ ] SR 앞에 IR Denoise가 없으면 `configs/data/sr_finetune_ir_sensor.yaml` 사용
  - [ ] SR 앞에 IR Denoise가 있으면 `configs/data/sr_finetune_ir_after_denoise.yaml` 사용

### EO Stage-2 실행 후보
```bash
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0 accelerate launch --num_processes=1 tools/train.py \
  --config configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_2x_dim32_block4_eo.yaml \
  --data_config configs/data/sr_finetune_eo_after_denoise.yaml
```

```bash
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 accelerate launch --num_processes=1 tools/train.py \
  --config configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_4x_dim32_block4_eo.yaml \
  --data_config configs/data/sr_finetune_eo_after_denoise.yaml
```

### IR Stage-2 실행 후보
```bash
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0 accelerate launch --num_processes=1 tools/train.py \
  --config configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_2x_dim32_block4_ir.yaml \
  --data_config configs/data/sr_finetune_ir_sensor.yaml
```

```bash
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 accelerate launch --num_processes=1 tools/train.py \
  --config configs/finetune/SVFocusSRNet/svfocussrnet_4x_dim32_block4_ir.yaml \
  --data_config configs/data/sr_finetune_ir_sensor.yaml
```

